name: Strange Movements #1257
description:
Strange Movements conjure the image of a watch movement, twisting back and forth and spiraling around as the movement measures time. Some movements pause for a brief moment to let you admire the intricate machinery, others keep going uninterrupted.

The Strange Movements series builds on the earlier t-SNE series [1] but adds the element of movement. Also, the rendering algorithm has been modified to produce somewhat different shapes.

Sources:

[1] https://clauswilke.com/art/project/t-sne
